### Health
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/health

### Series list
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/series

### Series detail
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/series/USDTRY

### Observations
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/series/USDTRY/observations?limit=30

### Latest
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/series/USDTRY/latest

### Dashboard summary
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/dashboard/summary

### Compare
GET http://localhost:8010/api/v1/compare?series=USDTRY,CPI&normalize=true

### Fetch data in local/dev
POST http://localhost:8010/api/v1/admin/fetch-data
